{"title":"手","authors":["杜妹芬"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":5,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜妹芬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友啊朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我年轻的朋友！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迢遥万里外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们向我招手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我挽住你们的臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我握住你们的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动的手，创造的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备向人类奉献的手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我看看你们的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有粉笔末，有墨痕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有福尔马林水渍……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是从来没有沾染鲜血啊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然没有在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香水餐巾上擦过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是曾经庄严地宣誓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样的手是干净的手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国：十一亿双手中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到底一共有几双"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玩弄阴谋的、与人民为敌的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罪恶的黑手？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月十七日黄昏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太平洋上机舱中"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}